OL,3,CBlood scandal: Government needs to act
OL,4,Cfaster to bring justice, say victims
OL,6,FTwo victims of the infected blood
OL,7,Fscandal have said more people will die
OL,8,Fwithout justice, the longer the
OL,9,FGovernment keeps them waiting for
OL,10,Fcompensation.JRichard Waring from
OL,11,FGunnislake and Kevin Roberts from
OL,12,FHayle, in Cornwall say they are "blood
OL,13,Fbrothers" after being infected with
OL,14,Fblood products, which led to them
OL,15,Fcontracting Hepatitis C.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,18,Fthey said the government is long
OL,19,Foverdue making reparations for all of
OL,20,Fthose affected.
