OL,3,CBlood scandal: Government needs to act
OL,4,Cfaster to bring justice, say victims
OL,6,F"I know we're four or five decades
OL,7,Fold, but I would like to see someone
OL,8,Fprosecuted," Kevin Roberts said.
OL,10,F"Be it the big pharmaceuticals, be the
OL,11,Fgovernment who allowed this poison to
OL,12,Fbe given to us or some of the doctors
OL,13,Fwho allowed this to happen. Shouldn't
OL,14,Fbe allowed to get away with it."
OL,16,FRichard Waring added: "People need to
OL,17,Fsee progress. The last few months, it
OL,18,Fhas been really frustrating because
OL,19,Fthere's been this blanket silence from
OL,20,Fthe Government. They just weren't
OL,21,Ftelling us what was going on."
