OL,3,CBlood scandal: Government needs to act
OL,4,Cfaster to bring justice, say victims
OL,6,FRichard's wife, Jacqueline, said
OL,7,Freceiving the news felt like "the
OL,8,Fbottom fell out of our world" and she
OL,9,Fhad fears for her future daughter.
OL,11,F"I was just about to have this baby
OL,12,Fand all your hopes and dreams of a
OL,13,Fyoung mum and starting a family.
OL,15,F"I knew there was a possibility our
OL,16,Fdaughter too could have a hep C. That
OL,17,Fmeans that the whole family could go."
OL,19,F"We were just absolutely traumatised,"
OL,20,FRichard added.
