OL,3,CBlood scandal: Government needs to act
OL,4,Cfaster to bring justice, say victims
OL,6,FAn interim report recommended a series
OL,7,Fof compensation payments, and in
OL,8,FOctober 2022 the Government announced
OL,9,Finterim payments of #100,000 for
OL,10,Finfected beneficiaries and bereaved
OL,11,Fpartners who were registered with any
OL,12,Fof the four UK-infected blood support
OL,13,Fschemes.
OL,15,FA government spokesperson said: "This
OL,16,Fwas an appalling tragedy, and our
OL,17,Fthoughts remain with all those
OL,18,Fimpacted.
